---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <section style="padding-top: 60px; border-bottom: none;">
        <div class="container reading" style="max-width: var(--container);">
            <span class="tag">Legal</span>
            <h1>Privacy <span class="highlight">Policy</span></h1>
            <p style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted);">Effective Date: June 2026</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding-top: 40px; border-bottom: none;">
        <div class="container reading" style="max-width: var(--container);">
            <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>This page explains how information is handled on this website.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Information Collection</h2>
            <p>This website does not actively collect personal information unless you choose to provide it. This may include:</p>
            <ul class="structural">
                <li>Name</li>
                <li>Email address</li>
                <li>Phone number</li>
                <li>Information submitted through contact forms, audit requests, or direct communication</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Use of Information</h2>
            <p>Information provided is used only for:</p>
            <ul class="structural">
                <li>Responding to inquiries</li>
                <li>Communication related to the request</li>
                <li>Delivering requested services</li>
                <li>Basic site functionality</li>
            </ul>
            <p>No information is used for profiling, targeting, or resale.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Cookies</h2>
            <p>This website may use basic cookies for functionality and performance. These cookies do not identify you personally. You can disable cookies through your browser settings.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p>This website may use third-party services such as:</p>
            <ul class="structural">
                <li>Analytics tools</li>
                <li>Hosting providers</li>
                <li>Email or communication services</li>
            </ul>
            <p>These services may collect anonymized usage data. Their policies are governed by their respective platforms.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Data Sharing</h2>
            <p>No personal information is sold, rented, or shared with third parties, except where required by law.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Data Security</h2>
            <p>Reasonable measures are taken to protect information. However, no system can guarantee absolute security.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">External Links</h2>
            <p>This website may contain links to external websites. This policy does not apply to those websites.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Changes</h2>
            <p>This policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Contact</h2>
            <p>For questions regarding this policy, please use the contact methods available through this website.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Boundary</h2>
            <p>This policy describes the information-handling practices of this website. It does not create additional obligations beyond what is stated here.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>